title: Synthesis of the originally proposed structure of elatenyne and an enyne from Laurencia majuscula
abstract: YesA bidirectional synthesis of the originally proposed structures for the natural products elatenyne and a chloroenyne from Laurencia majuscula is described along with a reassessment of the structures of the halogenated enynes based upon a 13C NMR chemical shift/structure correlationEPSRCErratum in: Org Biomol Chem. 2009 Dec 21;7(24):5271-2
